"use strict";(self.webpackChunkageno_blog=self.webpackChunkageno_blog||[]).push([[8923],{2143(i,s,e){e.r(s),e.d(s,{comp:()=>n,data:()=>h});var a=e(641);const l={},n=(0,e(6262).A)(l,[["render",function(i,s){return(0,a.uX)(),(0,a.CE)("div",null,[...s[0]||(s[0]=[(0,a.Fv)('<h1 id="_01-cmake-从-0-开始" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_01-cmake-从-0-开始"><span>01. CMake 从 0 开始</span></a></h1><h2 id="_1-cmake-是什么" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_1-cmake-是什么"><span>1. CMake 是什么</span></a></h2><p>写 C++ 程序时，最终要调用编译器，比如：</p><div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="bash" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-bash"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF;">c++</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379;"> src/01_hello_cmake.cpp</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66;"> -o</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379;"> 01_hello_cmake</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>但项目一大，就会有很多问题：</p><ul><li>源文件很多，命令很长。</li><li>头文件目录要手动写。</li><li>不同系统编译器不同。</li><li>Debug/Release 配置不同。</li><li>多个程序、多个库不好管理。</li></ul><p>CMake 的作用是：你写 <code>CMakeLists.txt</code> 描述项目结构，CMake 帮你生成真正的构建文件。</p><h2 id="_2-最小-cmakelists-txt" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_2-最小-cmakelists-txt"><span>2. 最小 CMakeLists.txt</span></a></h2><p>看本项目的 <a href="../CMakeLists.txt">CMakeLists.txt</a>。</p><p>最关键的是这几句：</p><div class="language-cmake line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="cmake" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-cmake"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">cmake_minimum_required</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(VERSION 3.16)</span></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">project</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(cmake_socket_from_zero LANGUAGES CXX)</span></span>\n<span class="line"></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">add_executable</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(01_hello_cmake src/01_hello_cmake.cpp)</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>含义：</p><ul><li><code>cmake_minimum_required</code>：要求最低 CMake 版本。</li><li><code>project</code>：定义项目名和语言。</li><li><code>add_executable</code>：生成一个可执行程序。</li></ul><p><code>add_executable(01_hello_cmake src/01_hello_cmake.cpp)</code> 的意思是：</p><ul><li>目标名字叫 <code>01_hello_cmake</code>。</li><li>它由 <code>src/01_hello_cmake.cpp</code> 编译而来。</li><li>编译成功后会得到 <code>build/01_hello_cmake</code>。</li></ul><h2 id="_3-为什么要用-build-目录" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_3-为什么要用-build-目录"><span>3. 为什么要用 build 目录</span></a></h2><p>推荐这样构建：</p><div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="bash" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-bash"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF;">cmake</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66;"> -S</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379;"> .</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66;"> -B</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379;"> build</span></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF;">cmake</span><span style="--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66;"> --build</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379;"> build</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>含义：</p><ul><li><code>-S .</code>：源码目录是当前目录。</li><li><code>-B build</code>：构建产物放到 <code>build/</code>。</li></ul><p>这样源码和编译生成的文件不会混在一起。</p><h2 id="_4-多个程序怎么写" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_4-多个程序怎么写"><span>4. 多个程序怎么写</span></a></h2><p>本项目有多个可执行程序：</p><div class="language-cmake line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="cmake" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-cmake"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">add_executable</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(02_tcp_server src/02_tcp_server.cpp)</span></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">add_executable</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(02_tcp_client src/02_tcp_client.cpp)</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>每写一个 <code>add_executable</code>，就多生成一个程序。</p><h2 id="_5-include-目录怎么用" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_5-include-目录怎么用"><span>5. include 目录怎么用</span></a></h2><p>本项目有：</p><div class="language-text line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="text" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-text"><span class="line"><span>include/common.hpp</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>所以 CMake 写了：</p><div class="language-cmake line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="cmake" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-cmake"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">include_directories</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">${CMAKE_CURRENT_SOURCE_DIR}</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">/include)</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>意思是告诉编译器：以后 <code>#include &quot;common.hpp&quot;</code> 时，去 <code>include/</code> 目录找。</p><p>初学阶段先这样写就够用。项目变复杂后，可以学习更现代的：</p><div class="language-cmake line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="cmake" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-cmake"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">target_include_directories</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(目标名 PRIVATE include)</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="_6-你应该记住的-cmake-模板" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_6-你应该记住的-cmake-模板"><span>6. 你应该记住的 CMake 模板</span></a></h2><p>初学时先背这个：</p><div class="language-cmake line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext="cmake" style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34;"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-cmake"><span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">cmake_minimum_required</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(VERSION 3.16)</span></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">project</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(my_project LANGUAGES CXX)</span></span>\n<span class="line"></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">set</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD 17)</span></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">set</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(CMAKE_CXX_STANDARD_REQUIRED </span><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">ON</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">)</span></span>\n<span class="line"></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">include_directories</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(</span><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">${CMAKE_CURRENT_SOURCE_DIR}</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">/include)</span></span>\n<span class="line"></span>\n<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">add_executable</span><span style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#ABB2BF;">(my_app src/main.cpp)</span></span></code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0;"><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p>能跑起来后，再慢慢理解每一行。</p>',37)])])}]]),h=JSON.parse('{"path":"/posts/C__/socket/01_cmake_from_zero.html","title":"01. CMake 从 0 开始","lang":"zh-CN","frontmatter":{},"git":{"createdTime":1779465307000,"updatedTime":1779466471000,"contributors":[{"name":"ageno","username":"ageno","email":"2519529119@qq.com","commits":2,"url":"https://github.com/ageno"}]},"readingTime":{"minutes":1.42,"words":425},"filePathRelative":"posts/C++/socket/01_cmake_from_zero.md","excerpt":"\\n<h2>1. CMake 是什么</h2>\\n<p>写 C++ 程序时，最终要调用编译器，比如：</p>\\n<div class=\\"language-bash line-numbers-mode\\" data-highlighter=\\"shiki\\" data-ext=\\"bash\\" style=\\"--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34\\"><pre class=\\"shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code\\"><code class=\\"language-bash\\"><span class=\\"line\\"><span style=\\"--shiki-light:#4078F2;--shiki-dark:#61AFEF\\">c++</span><span style=\\"--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379\\"> src/01_hello_cmake.cpp</span><span style=\\"--shiki-light:#986801;--shiki-dark:#D19A66\\"> -o</span><span style=\\"--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379\\"> 01_hello_cmake</span></span></code></pre>\\n<div class=\\"line-numbers\\" aria-hidden=\\"true\\" style=\\"counter-reset:line-number 0\\"><div class=\\"line-number\\"></div></div></div>"}')},6262(i,s){s.A=(i,s)=>{const e=i.__vccOpts||i;for(const[i,a]of s)e[i]=a;return e}}}]);